	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
		                <note type="regest">Empfiehlt einen vornehmen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Engländer</placeName>, der nach <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italien</placeName> reist und <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName> besuchen möchte.</note>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salus in domino nostro Iesu Christo.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fateor ego, vir ornatissime <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>, meam in scribendo tarditatem, sed quae de meo erga te amore et fide nihil imminuat.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In praesentia autem cur has ad te literas scribo, in caussa est <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglus</placeName> is, vir pietate, doctrina, generis nobilitate eximius, qui in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiam</placeName> profecturus relicta patria, uxore, liberis quoniam pro more magnorum virorum istac transeuntium te invisere statuit, nolui committere, ut sine his ad te meis veniret, ex quibus intelligeres, quo animo et erga te et praestantes viros <persName ref="p8298" cert="high">Borrhaus</persName> esset, non vero impellerere[?], ut in hunc virum tua humanitatis plena officia et studia declarares, quod nihil aliud esset quam currentem ad cursum incitare.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu vale, vir clarissime, et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8298" cert="high">Borrhaum</persName> in tuis amicis numera.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvere meo nomine omnes bonos apud te viros volo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8298" cert="high">Martinus Borrhaus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, suo in domino amico et fratri observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
